		   <table class="mform"  border="0" cellpadding="1" cellspacing="0" width="100%" >
		   <tr><td class="headerrow" colspan="2" class="mform" valign="top" id="forumSubject">Why Do You Like Your Job / Role?<br clear="all" /><script type="text/javascript">document.title = document.title + ": Thread: Why Do You Like Your Job / Role?";</script>
		   <span class="sm">Posted @ Thu, Mar 31st 11:06 AM2005 </span><span class="notbold">| <span class="sm">IP: Logged</span> | <a href="/forum.html?forum=62&mid=1112285175241255845&post=1"><a class="sm" href="/forum.html?forum=62&mid=1112285175241255845&num=23&page=0&post=1&replyto=1112285175241255845"><img src="/shared/reply_to_thread_ico.gif" border="0" alt="Reply..." height="11" width="17" /> Reply to this</a></a> | <a class="sm" href="/db/journal2.html?user=399528"><img border="0" src="/shared/user_journal.gif" border="0" height="12" width="17" /> User's Journal</a> | <a class=sm href="mailto:Wondroustremor@allakhazam.com"><img src="/shared/mail3.gif" border="0" height="10" width="17" /> Email User</a>  <a name=1112285175241255845></a></small></td></tr>
		   <tr><td valign="top" id="fs8" class="mform" ><span class="notbold">By:</span> <a href="/db/poster.html?user=399528"><span id="Sage">Wondroustremor</span></a><b><span id="Sage"><br>Sage</span></b><br /><img alt="Avatar" height="100" width="100" src="/uf/Wondroustremor/Galka_Claus.JPG"><br /><br /><img src="/shared/user_star_ico.gif" height="9" width="9" alt="*" /><img src="/shared/user_star_ico.gif" height="9" width="9" alt="*" /><br />748 posts
		   <br /><nobr><span class="notbold">Score</span>: Excellent [4.63]</nobr><br /><br /><a href="/cgi-bin/pm.pl?action=addtolist&addname=Wondroustremor&type=Address" id="fs8"><img src="/shared/plus.gif" border="0" align="middle" height="9" width="9" alt="Add to address book"> Add to address book</a><br /><img src="/shared/transp.gif" width="135" border="0" height="1"></td><td valign="top" class="mform" width="100%">
<p>After looking at the &quot;&lt;insertjobname&gt; sucks because&quot; threads that seem to proliferate the forums recently, I decided to think about why I really like my character- his job, what I do with him (it is an RPG after all), and how I play the game. <br /> <br />I'm mainly war/mnk (although I've also lvled thf and rng a bit).&nbsp;&nbsp;I love being a warrior, and I really love being a Galka.  I can take hits and take less damage.  I can smite mobs.  The way I play, I role-play a bit... but my character is also kind of an extension of myself.   <br /> <br />I try to be kind and honorable, helping who I can where I can.  However, when dealing with battles, I fight furiously.  I take it as a source of pride when I'm the main meat shield and I have kept hate so well that the backup tank can't pull the mob off me.  It's weird, and has sometimes resulted in my demise, but it's what I'm there for.  Nothing for me beats being able to pull a mob away from someone, give it a stern spanking, and get a <span style="color: lime;">{</span>bow<span style="color: red;">}</span> or <span style="color: lime;">{</span>Thank you.<span style="color: red;">}</span> in return. <br /> <br />So why do you like your job?  What do you enjoy best about it?  Discuss! <img border="0" src="/shared/smilies/boozing.gif" alt="icon"/></p>
<br /><span class="sm">----------------------------</span><br /><a href="HTTP://ffxi.allakhazam.com/profile.xml?46812 " title="HTTP://ffxi.allakhazam.com/profile.xml?46812 " target="akztarg">Wondroustremor</a>&nbsp;&nbsp;(Remora) <br />Linkshell: <a href="HTTP://bloodtribe.namastemassage.net" title="HTTP://bloodtribe.namastemassage.net" target="akztarg">BloodTribe</a> <br /><i>No matter how the wind howls, the mountain cannot bow to it.</i></td></td></tr><tr><td colspan="2" class="mform"><table border="0" cellspacing="0" cellpadding="0" width="100%"><tr><td id="fs8">Posting from Bermuda</td><td align="right" id="fs8" >23 Replies</td></tr></table>
</td></tr></table></td></tr><tr><td>

