		   <span class="sm">Posted @ Thu, Mar 31st 2:16 PM2005 </span><span class="notbold">| <span class="sm">IP: Logged</span> | <a class="sm" href="/forum.html?forum=62&mid=1112285175241255845&num=23&page=0&post=1&replyto=1112296527112688596"><img src="/shared/reply_to_thread_ico.gif" border="0" alt="Reply..." height="11" width="17" /> Reply to this</a></a>    <a name=1112296527112688596></a></small></td></tr>
		   <tr><td valign="top" id="fs8" class="mform2" ><span class="notbold">By:</span> <a href="/db/poster.html?user=343962"><span id="Scholar">Deadd</span></a><b><span id="Scholar"><br>Scholar</span></b><br />32 posts
		   <br /><nobr><span class="notbold">Score</span>: Decent [3.41]</nobr><br /><br /><a href="/cgi-bin/pm.pl?action=addtolist&addname=Deadd&type=Address" id="fs8"><img src="/shared/plus.gif" border="0" align="middle" height="9" width="9" alt="Add to address book"> Add to address book</a><br /><img src="/shared/transp.gif" width="135" border="0" height="1"></td><td valign="top" class="mform2" width="100%">
<p>I am really enjoying BST.  <br /> <br />I have the ability to solo things that made my War/Mnk run screaming like a little girl. No one complains about my sub, equip etc.. not that I had these issues before. But now if I want to go out as BST/Midet Circus Clown, I can.  <br /> <br />I get to visit and level in areas that I never went to as a 31 war. All the drops are mine.  <br /> <br />Sometimes though it gets lonely/boring. When I get feeling like that all I have to do is get in a pick-up party for about a 1/2 hour and I am usually more than happy to go back to beast :P.</p>
