<p>I love THF! For all of the reasons that have already been stated and probably a million more. It's a great job and, in my opinion, often an overlooked aspect of a succesful party. THF's are very versatile. They can heal themselves and weaken mobs with different bolts, end skillchains for enormous damage, lay large amounts of hate on tanks, set the flow of exp when pulling. I can go on and on. Although in my experience THF has gotten a bad rep(hopefully it's not because I'm not as good of a THF as I think I am). It is my main and I love it! <br /> <br />btw...if by chance we've partied together and you have constructive criticism for me, feel free to /tell me. Peace.</p>
